result.execSummary:
The defendant Daniel R Kelsey was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Daniel R Kelsey is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Daniel R Kelsey was found guilty of Possession of Narcotic Drugs, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(am).
